description:
Jesus promised that He would return. In this inspiring sermon Cami Oetman explores the various Bible prophecies that have already happened and points out the greatest promise ever made: "I will return that you may be where I am."

Are you ready to make a decision to be baptized as a disciple of Jesus Christ? Visit http://bible.awr.org and we will be with you every step of the way.

This is the second episode in the AWR Master Class series called Unlocking Bible Prophecies 2.0. You can follow the series and interact LIVE at: 

http://awr.org/bible

THE SIGNS
This question has perplexed thinkers throughout history. In fact, right before His death, Jesus disciples questioned Him about this very thing. In Matthew 24:3, they asked, When shall these things be? And what shall be the sign of Thy coming, and of the end of the world? The disciples were gathered on the Mount of Olives, overlooking the temple of Jerusalem. In their minds, the destruction of Jerusalem and the end of the world would happen simultaneously. Jesus had talked about the destruction of Jerusalem, and they wanted to know more. As Jesus answered their questions, He shared events that would transpire before His return.

Don't be scared by the signs of His soon coming. Jesus offers hope. He offers salvation. He offers you a relationship with Him that will protect you from deception. His heart longs for you to make the decision to choose Him. He came to this earth and became the Son of Man to show us the way to live so that we could join Him for eternity.

As you discover Bible prophecy and discern the signs of Christs soon return, would you like to acknowledge, Yes, Jesus, I believe You are coming soon? Do you want to be ready for the great day of His coming?

Is there anything in your life that would keep you from being ready? Its time to surrender that thing to Jesus. Its time to accept His invitation of hope and peace.

Have questions? Need prayer? Visit us at http://bible.awr.org
